OL,4,G2000FLost Cities of the Ancients
OL,5,     GDocumentary series which unearths
OL,6,     Glost civilisations and cities.
OL,7,     GThis edition visits northern Peru
OL,8,     Gto find the ruins of 250
OL,9,     Gmysterious pyramids.
OL,10,G2100FDa Vinci: The Lost Treasure
OL,11,     GFiona Bruce uncovers the story of
OL,12,     GLeonardo da Vinci. She travels to
OL,13,     GFlorence, Milan, Paris, Warsaw
OL,14,     Gand to New York, where she is
OL,15,     Ggiven an exclusive preview of a
OL,16,     Gnew Leonardo.
